oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: George Jones, Tammy Wynette, and Harold Morrison
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Jones, George, 1931-2013; Hubert Long Talent Agency; Morrison, Harold; Offset printing; Wynette, Tammy;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising The George Jones - Tammy Wynette Show featuring Grand Ole Opry stars George Jones and Tammy Wynette with Harold Morrison and the Jones Boys, available through Hubert Long Agency. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
